Additionally, the paper involves the use of polycube maps, which are commonly used in Computer Vision (cs.CV) for mesh generation. The optimization technique used in the paper is gradient-based, which is a common approach in Neural Networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper may also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category due to its focus on shape optimization.
